Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:32.64,isong_sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}啊 请一定要告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:48.51,isong_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}人は何故　傷つけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:48.51,isong_sc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fad(300,300)}人们为何互相伤害彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫涅鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是集的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来 律师会晤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 集同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是接受你母亲委托
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来给你辩护的梅森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 开始侵入主系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间挺紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在方便说话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摄像头和麦克已经屏蔽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 全员开始待命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不容易啊 很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交给我吧 一定会把你弄出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说我是笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某人被关在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来营救他的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城户研二 那个杀人犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大云他们这就开始进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出去后马上去地下的单间牢房 跟城户汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后取出他的Void
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后在30秒内…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想当然地命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们跟你说什么了 谁跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所长戈尔迪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 涯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有工作人员注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系统被人入侵已经崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在使用预备阵列进行重启
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再播报一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小云 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行对空防御
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派出End Rave！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾姐 确认敌机启动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解 我这也准备OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,角度和方向都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,办得到吗 绫瀬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时听候差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了 快决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是前行 还是原地踏步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去你那 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要来这？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你待命吗 你怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯 确定祈的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单独侵入了设施内部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且正在下载集囚房所在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈是打算救集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 我不在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 她切断了通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在塔那边防守非常严密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会晤结束了 快回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许动 抵抗的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 给我呼叫四分仪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了 涯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在撤离 我把绫瀬送进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了意外情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我单独去营救城户
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了 涯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫瀬按原计划出动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她掩护集和祈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四分仪先生 斯坦纳出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集 祈 求你们了 别乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯 城户的位置变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好机会 告诉我位置信息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓获逃跑中的囚犯 正在识别号码 紧急情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对祈做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那她怎么可能会违抗涯的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你 作战全乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涯要有个三长两短 绝不放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少佐 第四隔离设施长发来联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「设施由我们自己保护到底 不用插手」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解 那我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他们说不用插手…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然不会插手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是看看 看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥一定保护好你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安心睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 去躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城户研二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 这家伙的力量就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城户研二的Void可以操纵重力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我赶上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈 我可以相信你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城户在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫瀬 带他回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法决定的话 相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都交给我吧 但也要服从于我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:25.45,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}もうあなたから愛されることも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:25.45,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}已经不再被你爱护着
