Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:38.76,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}我就这样 独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.20,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}落ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.20,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:48.73,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}あの時あなたはなんて言ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:48.73,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}那时的你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:55.42,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}届かない言葉は宙を舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:55.42,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}无法传达的言语早已飘逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:22:02.09,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}分かってるのに　今日もしてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:22:02.09,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}虽然心里明白  却又一如从前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.73,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}叶わぬ 願いことを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.73,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}许下那  无法实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:15.44,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}はなさないで　ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:15.44,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}请不要放手 紧紧地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.82,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}手を握ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.82,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:25.66,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}あなたと二人つづくと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:25.66,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}说好了两人将携手同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:34.65,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}繋いだ　その手は暖かくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:34.65,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}牵着我的那双手是如此温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:42.77,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}優しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:42.77,ed_sc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.75}如此柔和